<span id="Description"></span>
== Описание ==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The [[Image:Sketcher_CreatePeriodicBSplineByInterpolation.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_CreatePeriodicBSplineByInterpolation|Sketcher CreatePeriodicBSplineByInterpolation]] tool creates a periodic (closed) [[B-Splines|B-spline]] curve by knot points. {{Version|1.0}}: This is the same tool as [[Sketcher_CreateBSpline|Sketcher CreateBSpline]] but with a different initial mode.
</div>

